   <text:p text:style-name="P707"> Nu <text:s/>l-ai <text:s/>omort <text:s/>tu! <text:s/>Caut-i <text:s/>altul. <text:s/>Ce <text:s/>stai <text:s/>piatr <text:s/>pe capul nostru </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P707"> Caut-i <text:s/>alt <text:s/>brbat, <text:s/>dad, <text:s/>se <text:s/>amestec <text:s/>n vorb Dumitrache, nvlegul. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Are musti rocovane pe buz Dumitrache, i nas mare, vulturesc. Are ochi galbeni de arpe. </text:p>
