   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Coboar poteca. Are doi frai n satul care se vede, oameni cu stare, negustori. La care s se duc? Fraii s-au glcevit. Muierile <text:s/>i-au <text:s/>ndemnat <text:s/>s <text:s/>se <text:s/>cioroviasc. Cel <text:s/>mai <text:s/>mare, Lisandru, <text:s/>e <text:s/>bolnav <text:s/>de <text:s/>piept. <text:s/>Nevast-sa, <text:s/>femeie <text:s/>de <text:s/>la <text:s/>ora, tromete i ea. Le-a rmas un copil,<text:span text:style-name="T6"> </text:span>Iancu, uscat, slbnog, ligav <text:s/>i <text:s/>lingav, <text:s/>parc <text:s/>ar <text:s/>mnca <text:s/>cenu, <text:s/>nu <text:s/>prinde <text:s/>carne <text:s/>pe el. Le hrie tusea-n piept la toi. Ru Lisandru, rea nevast-sa. <text:s/>Totui, <text:s/>parc <text:s/>e <text:s/>mai <text:s/>bun Lisandru dect <text:s/>Tone. <text:s/>Acela <text:s/>are trei <text:s/>copii, <text:s/>trei <text:s/>fete, <text:s/>i-n <text:s/>fiecare <text:s/>primvar, <text:s/>cu burta <text:s/>la <text:s/>gur, nevast-sa, <text:s/>Finica, <text:s/>st <text:s/>gata <text:s/>s <text:s/>nasc. <text:s/>Iad <text:s/>casa <text:s/>lui <text:s/>Tone. Femeia <text:s/>ip <text:s/>s <text:s/>fie <text:s/>dus <text:s/>la <text:s/>ora, <text:s/>nu-i <text:s/>place <text:s/>la <text:s/>ar, <text:s/>nu <text:s/>e-nvat <text:s/>s triasc <text:s/>la <text:s/>ar. <text:s/>Ce <text:s/>s <text:s/>fac <text:s/>Tone <text:s/>la <text:s/>ora? <text:s/>N-a adunat nc destui bani s poat deschide prvlie la trg </text:p>
