   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> De, <text:s/>mi, <text:s/>bani <text:s/>avea, <text:s/>i <text:s/>nu <text:s/>puini <text:s/>Cine <text:s/>l-a <text:s/>pus <text:s/>s <text:s/>se in de mine, s m omoare? Am luat chimirul, cu galbeni cu tot. Era un chimir lat, rocat, nituit cu bani de<text:span text:style-name="T8"> </text:span>aram </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">Deliormanul, <text:s/>pdurea <text:s/>nebun <text:s/>S-a <text:s/>dus <text:s/>pdurea nebun Lng Adncata, i aveau btrnii priscile. Toamna <text:s/>se <text:s/>duceau, <text:s/>fumreau <text:s/>stupii, <text:s/>storceau mierea <text:s/>din <text:s/>faguri, <text:s/>o <text:s/>aduceau <text:s/>la <text:s/>bordeie <text:s/>n <text:s/>putinici <text:s/>de stejar. <text:s/>Mncau <text:s/>copiii <text:s/>mierea <text:s/>Dac <text:s/>mncau <text:s/>mult, <text:s/>le curgea mierea pe buric </text:p>
