   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Ce <text:s/>s <text:s/>crezi?! <text:s/>Tu <text:s/>nu <text:s/>crezi <text:s/>nimic. <text:s/>Eti <text:s/>ca <text:s/>Toma necredinciosul. <text:s/>Vrei <text:s/>s <text:s/>vezi <text:s/>totul, <text:s/>cu <text:s/>ochii <text:s/>ti <text:s/>Api, maic, s tii, nimeni nu vede tot. Trebuie s mai i crezi Te scalzi la grl, vara? </text:p>
