   <text:p text:style-name="P212">Btrnul <text:s/>cioplete <text:s/>n <text:s/>lemn <text:s/>de <text:s/>nuc <text:s/>i <text:s/>scoate <text:s/>din <text:s/>minile lui <text:s/>cruci <text:s/>mici, <text:s/>pe <text:s/>care <text:s/>ncrusteaz <text:s/>semne <text:s/>ciudate. <text:s/>n captul <text:s/>de <text:s/>jos <text:s/>al <text:s/>crucii <text:s/>sap <text:s/>litere <text:s/>pe <text:s/>care <text:s/>nu <text:s/>pot <text:s/>s <text:s/>le citesc. </text:p>
