   <text:p text:style-name="P235">Ct casa, nmeii. Nu mai ninge, nici soarele nu se vede </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P236">Ciucii n cas, pe lng sob, stm ct putem. Ni se urte, lum <text:s/>zdrene <text:s/>pe <text:s/>noi, <text:s/>mai <text:s/>ieim <text:s/>puin <text:s/>pe <text:s/>uli. <text:s/>S-au <text:s/>croit pretutindeni <text:s/>prtii. <text:s/>Cteodat, <text:s/>seara, <text:s/>vine <text:s/>un <text:s/>vtel <text:s/>de <text:s/>la primrie, <text:s/>bate <text:s/>cu <text:s/>ciomagul <text:s/>n <text:s/>poart. <text:s/>Cinii, <text:s/>pe <text:s/>el, <text:s/>s-l sfie.</text:p>
