   <text:p text:style-name="P242">A <text:s/>cules <text:s/>tata <text:s/>zdrene, <text:s/>boarfe <text:s/>vechi, <text:s/>saci <text:s/>rupi, <text:s/>a <text:s/>nvelit <text:s/>n coar boii, caii. Cinilor le curg ochii. Le-am fcut culcu n tind, <text:s/>culcu <text:s/>de <text:s/>paie. <text:s/>Am <text:s/>adus <text:s/>n <text:s/>cas <text:s/>ginile <text:s/>i <text:s/>capra <text:s/>cu barb, ciut, de la care mulgem, vara, dup ce<text:span text:style-name="T54"> </text:span>njunghie<text:span text:style-name="T54"> </text:span>miedul cu cornie abia rsrite  dou noduri ca doi nsturai negri  o ulcic de lapte.</text:p>
