   <text:p text:style-name="P252">Aa <text:s/>s-a <text:s/>i <text:s/>ntmplat. <text:s/>Porumbul, <text:s/>pn <text:s/>la <text:s/>genunchi <text:s/>a crescut, <text:s/>apoi <text:s/>s-a <text:s/>scorojit <text:s/>i <text:s/>el, <text:s/>n-a <text:s/>prins <text:s/>floare, <text:s/>n-a <text:s/>prin legtur. <text:s/>Spre <text:s/>toamn <text:s/>cmpurile, <text:s/>satele <text:s/>erau <text:s/>negre, arse.<text:span text:style-name="T58"> </text:span>Trecuse peste ele prjolul duman al soarelui. </text:p>
