   <text:p text:style-name="P267">Ne cad n vatr neamurile din ctun. i nclzesc, la focul de <text:s/>paie <text:s/>care <text:s/>scoate <text:s/>fum <text:s/>gros <text:s/>i <text:s/>negru, <text:s/>minile <text:s/>mari, noduroase, asprite i mai mult de gerul nprasnic. </text:p>
