   <text:p text:style-name="P269">Muierea, mititic, fcut ghem, vorbete, se cineaz i se uit <text:s/>cu <text:s/>ochii <text:s/>stini <text:s/>n <text:s/>flacra <text:s/>galben, <text:s/>puin, <text:s/>a <text:s/>focului. Vru-meu <text:s/>Dumitru <text:s/>Plic <text:s/>tace. <text:s/>Tace <text:s/>i <text:s/>tata. <text:s/>Boabele porumbului sunt ca i numrate, socotite s ne ajung pn s-or topi zpezile. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P270"> N-am pus nimic n gur de dou zile. Noi ca noi!<text:span text:style-name="T62"> </text:span>Pcat de copii! mai spune muierea. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P270">Mama, <text:s/>tras <text:s/>la <text:s/>fa, <text:s/>galben, <text:s/>se <text:s/>ridic. <text:s/>Ia <text:s/>o <text:s/>desag. <text:line-break/>O<text:span text:style-name="T61"> </text:span>umple cu mlai. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P270"> D-mi orul, Mario, s-i pun i un gvan de fin, s faci copiilor o cocoace, s fie de sufletul morilor. </text:p>
