   <text:p text:style-name="P405">Unde s-o fi ascuns notarul? Unde s-o fi ascuns primarul? Primria <text:s/>e <text:s/>goal. <text:s/>i <text:s/>caut <text:s/>oamenii <text:s/>i <text:s/>nu-i <text:s/>gsesc.<text:span text:style-name="T97"> </text:span>Aflm <text:s/>c eful <text:s/>postului <text:s/>de <text:s/>jandarmi <text:s/>st <text:s/>la <text:s/>gar <text:s/>de <text:s/>paz, <text:s/>cu <text:s/>puca ncrcat. <text:s/>N-avem <text:s/>nicio <text:s/>treab <text:s/>la <text:s/>gar. <text:s/>l <text:s/>lsm <text:s/>s-i piard vremea acolo.</text:p>
