   <text:p text:style-name="P408">Cnd <text:s/>doarme, <text:s/>doarme <text:s/>cu <text:s/>capul <text:s/>pe ciomag. Parc ar avea chimirul plin cu galbeni i s-ar teme ca <text:s/>nu <text:s/>cumva <text:s/>s <text:s/>vin <text:s/>cineva <text:s/>s <text:s/>i-l <text:s/>fure. <text:s/>Ce <text:s/>e <text:s/>pe <text:s/>el, <text:s/>i <text:s/>pe culme <text:s/>Mai <text:s/>are <text:s/>ceva, <text:s/>nevast <text:s/>i <text:s/>cinci <text:s/>copii, <text:s/>opincile sparte, zbunul rupt, crpit, ndragii  petic de petic. </text:p>
