   <text:p text:style-name="P654">De pe valea Oltului ne-a czut oaspete numai unchi-meu Gbunea, <text:s/>cu <text:s/>aa <text:s/>Aretia, <text:s/>nevast-sa. <text:s/>De <text:s/>pe <text:s/>Clmui <text:s/>au sosit surorile i nepoatele tatii. Unde o s-i mai culcm! i culcm <text:s/>pe <text:s/>la <text:s/>megiei, <text:s/>pe <text:s/>la <text:s/>oameni <text:s/>din <text:s/>sat <text:s/>Odat <text:s/>se mrit sor-mea Evanghelina! O dat i facem nunt! </text:p>
