   <text:p text:style-name="P704">Cu alde Misirliu c au, ca i noi, zece brae de munc.<text:span text:style-name="T157"> </text:span>Cu alde Uie, c sunt harnici: doi lucreaz ct ar lucra patru.</text:p>
