   <text:p text:style-name="P704"> Atunci, <text:s/>bine, <text:s/>te <text:s/>lum <text:s/>n <text:s/>ceat. <text:s/>La <text:s/>treierat <text:s/>ne-om descurca noi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P704"> Mulumim</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P704">Mergem <text:s/>la <text:s/>secerat <text:s/>tocmai <text:s/>pe <text:s/>Buduleasa, <text:s/>o <text:s/>jumtate <text:s/>de pot <text:s/>cu <text:s/>carul. <text:s/>Pe <text:s/>la <text:s/>miezul <text:s/>nopii <text:s/>ne <text:s/>trezim. <text:s/>Tot <text:s/>satul <text:s/>se trezete. Cocoii ne trezesc  cocoii, ori grija s nu ntrziem i s dm de bucluc cu boierul </text:p>
