   <text:p text:style-name="P707">Elisabeta plnge totdeauna cnd ne cheam mama la lut. O potolete spunndu-i mereu aceeai poveste. A fost odat o <text:s/>fat <text:s/>fr <text:s/>minte, <text:s/>care <text:s/>nu <text:s/>era <text:s/>cuminte. <text:s/>Nu <text:s/>se <text:s/>lsa <text:s/>s-o <text:s/>laie maic-sa. <text:s/>Au <text:s/>npdit-o <text:s/>pduchii. <text:s/>O <text:s/>sumedenie <text:s/>de <text:s/>pduchi <text:bookmark text:name="239"/>au <text:s/>crescut <text:s/>n <text:s/>prul <text:s/>ei. <text:s/>S-au <text:s/>vorbit <text:s/>pduchii. <text:s/>S-au <text:s/>fcut funie <text:s/>i-au <text:s/>trt <text:s/>fata <text:s/>la <text:s/>grl. <text:s/>Au <text:s/>bgat-o <text:s/>n <text:s/>grl <text:s/>i-au necat-o.</text:p>
