   <text:p text:style-name="P707">Intr i mama n cas. i mpletete cozile. Are prul ca paiul <text:s/>orzului, <text:s/>lung <text:s/>pn <text:s/>la <text:s/>olduri, <text:s/>mai <text:s/>jos <text:s/>de olduri.<text:span text:style-name="T158"> </text:span>Altdat era tnr. Pe Elisabeta o purta n brae. Pe mine m purta pe umeri. I se bttorise pielea pe umr cum <text:s/>se <text:s/>bttorete <text:s/>ceafa <text:s/>boului <text:s/>la <text:s/>jug. <text:s/>Umbla <text:s/>cu <text:s/>noi <text:s/>pe unde avea treab. Ceilali se ineau cu minile de fusta ei, dup ea, ca puii dup cloc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P707">Mama <text:s/>a <text:s/>rmas <text:s/>tot <text:s/>nalt. <text:s/>Dar <text:s/>nu <text:s/>mai <text:s/>e <text:s/>subire. <text:s/>I <text:s/>s-a ngroat <text:s/>mijlocul. <text:s/>Iar <text:s/>o <text:s/>s <text:s/>nasc. <text:s/>Se <text:s/>culc <text:s/>lng Elisabeta.<text:span text:style-name="T158"> </text:span>Lng <text:s/>Elisabeta <text:s/>m <text:s/>culc <text:s/>i <text:s/>eu, <text:s/>dincolo <text:s/>de <text:s/>mine ceilali.<text:span text:style-name="T158"> </text:span>Tata se mai culc i pe jos, ca s avem noi loc mai mult n pat.</text:p>
