   <text:p text:style-name="P707">Mamei nu-i prea place cnd vine mtu-mea Stana pe la noi. <text:s/>i <text:s/>mpuie <text:s/>capul <text:s/>cu <text:s/>vrute <text:s/>i <text:s/>nevrute. <text:s/>Asta <text:s/>n-ar <text:s/>fi <text:s/>nimic. Pacostea e alta. Cere un cuit i-ncepe s scobeasc vatra ori estul n care coceam pinea. Scobete cu vrful cuitului i scoate <text:s/>bucele <text:s/>de <text:s/>pmnt <text:s/>ars, <text:s/>gloduri <text:s/>roii, <text:s/>pe <text:s/>care <text:s/>le ronie ntre dini, le mestec i le nghite. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P707">Uche, <text:s/>dac <text:s/>nu <text:s/>mnnc <text:s/>pmnt <text:s/>ars, <text:s/>nu <text:s/>se <text:s/>simte <text:s/>stul. n fiecare zi mnnc Uche pmnt ars. Prin toate casele pe unde se duce, scobete vatra, scobete mai ales estul, care e scorojit de flcri. </text:p>
