   <text:p text:style-name="P707">Apa <text:s/>o <text:s/>nclzete <text:s/>sor-mea <text:s/>Evanghelina, <text:s/>care <text:s/>i-a <text:s/>adus fetia <text:s/>adormit <text:s/>n <text:s/>brae. <text:s/>M <text:s/>uit <text:s/>la <text:s/>amndou: <text:s/>o <text:s/>ppu mare legnnd la piept o ppu mai mic Ne scot n tind pe noi, copiii, Petria i Uche. Ne scot n tind <text:s/>s <text:s/>n-o <text:s/>mai <text:s/>vedem <text:s/>pe <text:s/>mama <text:s/>cum <text:s/>se <text:s/>zbate, <text:s/>s <text:s/>n-o auzim cum geme. N-o mai vedem. De auzit, o auzim. Geme din ce n ce mai tare. Mciuc ni se face prul. Carnea pe noi se-ncrnceneaz, se zburlete. Ne cuprinde frigul. De la ur <text:s/>aducem <text:s/>paie <text:s/>cu <text:s/>coul. <text:s/>Ne <text:s/>tolnim <text:s/>pe <text:s/>paie, <text:s/>ncercm<text:span text:style-name="T158"> </text:span>s adormim. </text:p>
