   <text:p text:style-name="P707">La <text:s/>mama <text:s/>nu <text:s/>se <text:s/>mai <text:s/>uit <text:s/>nimeni. <text:s/>Alb <text:s/>ca <text:s/>hrtia, <text:s/>lung, deirat, <text:s/>subire, <text:s/>zace <text:s/>n <text:s/>pat <text:s/>acoperit <text:s/>cu <text:s/>un <text:s/>ol. <text:s/>Parc doarme. <text:s/>Se <text:s/>apropie <text:s/>de <text:s/>ea <text:s/>tata. <text:s/>i <text:s/>srut <text:s/>obrazul. <text:s/>Mama deschide ochii. Zmbete: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P707"> A fost greu </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P707">Ct <text:s/>a <text:s/>stat <text:s/>la <text:s/>noi, <text:s/>Uche <text:s/>a <text:s/>scociort <text:s/>cu <text:s/>vrful <text:s/>cuitului <text:s/>i ne-a <text:s/>mncat <text:s/>vatra. <text:s/>Ne-a <text:s/>mncat <text:s/>i <text:s/>un <text:s/>sfert <text:s/>din <text:s/>est Dac-i <text:s/>place <text:s/>ei <text:s/>s <text:s/>mnnce <text:s/>pmnt <text:s/>O <text:s/>s <text:s/>lipim <text:s/>vatra <text:s/>la loc. O s schimbm estul. Mai avem cteva sub ptul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P707">A rmas bolnav mama, cu oasele desfcute. Nu se poate da <text:s/>jos <text:s/>din <text:s/>pat. <text:s/>Nu <text:s/>poate <text:s/>duce <text:s/>cana <text:s/>cu <text:s/>ap <text:s/>la <text:s/>gur. Cnd trebuie <text:s/>totui <text:s/>s <text:s/>se <text:s/>mite, <text:s/>o <text:s/>apucm <text:s/>de <text:s/>mijloc, <text:s/>i-o ajutm </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P707"> Ce te doare, mam? </text:p>
