   <text:p text:style-name="P708">De <text:s/>ciud <text:s/>c <text:s/>ai <text:s/>ncercat <text:s/>s <text:s/>scapi <text:s/>nejefuit, <text:s/>te <text:s/>dezbrcau <text:s/>la piele, <text:s/>te <text:s/>zdrobeau <text:s/>n <text:s/>ciomege, <text:s/>te <text:s/>lsau <text:s/>lat <text:s/>la <text:s/>marginea drumului <text:s/>i <text:s/>o <text:s/>luau <text:s/>spre <text:s/>adncul <text:s/>pdurii. <text:s/>Pn <text:s/>la <text:s/>ziu ateptai <text:s/>ali <text:s/>cltori <text:s/>s <text:s/>te <text:s/>ridice, <text:s/>s <text:s/>te <text:s/>oblojeasc. <text:s/>Hoii <text:s/>se ascundeau n tainiele lor</text:p>
