   <text:p text:style-name="P708">I <text:s/>s-a <text:s/>umplut <text:s/>oala <text:s/>de <text:s/>bani. <text:s/>S-a <text:s/>revrsat. <text:s/>Avocatul <text:s/>a <text:s/>dat sfoar-n <text:s/>ar <text:s/>c <text:s/>e <text:s/>amator <text:s/>s <text:s/>cumpere <text:s/>pmnt. <text:s/>Unde <text:s/>se afl <text:s/>o <text:s/>bucat <text:s/>de <text:s/>pmnt <text:s/> <text:s/>bun, <text:s/>rea, <text:s/>aproape, <text:s/>departe <text:s/> avocatul <text:s/>Vic <text:s/>Georgescu <text:s/>o <text:s/>cumpr. <text:s/>i <text:s/>muncesc <text:s/>toate aceste pmnturi, pe gratis, clienii.</text:p>
