   <text:p text:style-name="P708">A <text:s/>apucat <text:s/>doctorul <text:s/>Ganciu <text:s/>instrumentele <text:s/>i <text:s/>a <text:s/>mcelrit mortul <text:s/>ca <text:s/>pe <text:s/>o <text:s/>vit. <text:s/>Pe <text:s/>urm <text:s/>l-a <text:s/>cusut. <text:s/>Apoi <text:s/>s-a <text:s/>splat <text:s/>pe <text:bookmark text:name="291"/>mini.</text:p>
