   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:bookmark text:name="647"/><text:s/><text:line-break/>Saulina, cea oache i voinic, bgau de seam c-mi dau <text:line-break/>toat osteneala i c nu sunt cu nimic vinovat de lipsa de <text:line-break/>rvn la nvtur a odraslei lor i m miluiau din cnd n <text:line-break/>cnd <text:s/>cu <text:s/>o <text:s/>bncu, <text:s/>ori <text:s/>chiar <text:s/>cu <text:s/>un <text:s/>leu-doi, <text:s/>ceea <text:s/>ce <text:s/>era <text:line-break/>pentru <text:s/>mine <text:s/>i <text:s/>pentru <text:s/>ai <text:s/>mei <text:s/>o <text:s/>adevrat <text:s/>avere, <text:s/>sau <text:s/>mi <text:line-break/>aruncau <text:s/>un <text:s/>covrig <text:s/>ori <text:s/>o <text:s/>punguli <text:s/>cu <text:s/>rocove. <text:s/>Covrigul <text:s/>i <text:line-break/>rocovele le roniam ndat, dar banii i adunam cu grij. <text:line-break/>Aa <text:s/>se <text:s/>fcuse <text:s/>c <text:s/>n <text:s/>iarna <text:s/>aceea <text:s/>strnsesem <text:s/>douzeci <text:s/>i <text:line-break/>ceva de lei, o sum grozav de mare, pe care nu tiu dac, <text:line-break/>n <text:s/>afar <text:s/>de <text:s/>bogtani, <text:s/>de <text:s/>pop, <text:s/>de <text:s/>nvtor <text:s/>i <text:s/>de <text:s/>notar, <text:s/>o <text:line-break/>mai <text:s/>avea <text:s/>careva <text:s/>n <text:s/>cas <text:s/>n <text:s/>tot <text:s/>satul, <text:s/>i <text:s/>artasem <text:s/>comoara <text:line-break/>tatei. <text:line-break/> Dar <text:s/>tu <text:s/>eti <text:s/>bogat, <text:s/>Darie. <text:s/>Cu <text:s/>banii <text:s/>tia <text:s/>am <text:s/>putea <text:s/>s <text:line-break/>ne <text:s/>cumprm <text:s/>bilete <text:s/>de <text:s/>tren <text:s/>i <text:s/>s <text:s/>mergem <text:s/>dincolo <text:line-break/>dePloieti, <text:s/>la <text:s/>Muru <text:s/>s-l <text:s/>vedem <text:s/>pe <text:s/>frate-tu <text:s/>Gheorghe. <text:s/>De <text:line-break/>civa <text:s/>ani <text:s/>e <text:s/>pop. <text:s/>Nu <text:s/>ne <text:s/>mai <text:s/>scrie. <text:s/>Poate <text:s/>c <tex